### Execution checklist (verify before finishing)

- [ ] Every targeted `src/` file has analysis + `FEATURE_MAP` row
- [ ] Every page/feature has **eight** `*.smoke|ui|form|api|error|edge|mobile|accessibility.spec.ts` files (not one mega-file)
- [ ] `automation-tests/fixtures/mock-data/<slug>.data.ts` exists with **valid / invalid / edge / api**
- [ ] Specs import mock data; no `foo` / `bar` / `test123`
- [ ] `FORM_COVERAGE_TABLE` + `UNTESTED_FORMS: 0`
- [ ] CRUD/search/filter/pagination minimums met when those behaviors exist
- [ ] API: success, 404/4xx, 500, network abort, slow/timeout where applicable
- [ ] `automation-tests/index.ts` imports all new specs
- [ ] Selectors: `getByTestId` / `getByRole` / `getByLabel` / `getByPlaceholder` only (no CSS/XPath when avoidable)
- [ ] No `page.waitForTimeout()`
- [ ] Full Playwright run is green
